  "description": {
    "zh": "又见面了！\n好消息，你提供的关于撤离点的信息帮助我们获得了更多关于俄军在塔科夫活动的情报。\n\n那么接下来，我有个联系人可能会组织一批人去接近那儿的高阶军官，但他们缺少合适的装备，特别是头盔和防弹背心。具体来说是6B47头盔（有无伪装均可）和数码丛林迷彩背心。\n\n这任务不算太难，一些本地人可能带着这些装备。我不在乎你从哪里弄到这些东西，只要它们的状态尚可就行。我推荐你还是省点钱吧，别老想着去购买这些装备，不过你说了算。祝你好运。",
    "en": "Hello again!\nGood news, the information you brought us about the extraction points helped us gain more knowledge about the Russian army's current business in Tarkov.\n\nSo heres what's next, I have a contact that might be able to gather a few people to get close to high ranking officers, however he's missing the proper gear for them, helmets and vests specifically. It should be 6B47 helmets with or without cover and vests in digital flora. Shouldn't be too difficult.\n\nSome of the local bandits might be carrying them, however I don't care where you get the stuff from as long as it's in an acceptable condition. And I advise you not to buy any of the required pieces, but that is your choice, I recommend to save your money.\n\nGood luck out there."
  },
